    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あれは……クルーザー！？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁ……ああ、SOSに気付いたみたいですね",
      "startTime": 3.5201589744,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "SOS？ そんなものいつの間に……",
      "startTime": 11.3479822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "草や木の枝を集めてもらったでしょ？\nあれを使って、ここ以外の二ヶ所で火を起こしたんです",
      "startTime": 18.8000002067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "救難信号は『三』がポイントですから\n三ヶ所で煙を出しておいたんですよ",
      "startTime": 26.4000002067,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いつの間にそんなことを……",
      "startTime": 29.2125169278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "ん～……いい休暇になりましたね",
      "startTime": 31.8348077377,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃ、出る準備をしましょうか\n忘れ物しないで下さいね",
      "startTime": 40.666667382,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁぁ～……海風が気持ちいい～\n仕事とサバイバルで疲れた体に染みるぅ～",
      "startTime": 48.8333340486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "これで一安心ですね\nあ、メッセージが大量に溜まってるな……",
      "startTime": 56.0000007153,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "マネージャー業も大変ですね。ほんの数時間\n電波の届かない所にいただけでそんな状態になるなんて",
      "startTime": 63.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "というか{user}さん\n無人島にいる間、一睡もしてないですよね？",
      "startTime": 70.7333299796,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "私の方が働いてましたけど\n寝ずに見張ってくれたのは助かりました",
      "startTime": 78.0999951203,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "仕事もいいですけど、たまには休んで下さいね\n今後のマネジメントのためにも",
      "startTime": 85.5333269278,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（さっきまであんな過酷な状況だったのに）\n（平然としてる……心身共に、本当に強いんだな）",
      "startTime": 90.9333254019,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7650.863798599999,
          "startTime": 98.5841892005
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_way_night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "やっと帰って来れたー\n事務所に戻ると、不思議と落ち着きますね",
      "startTime": 103.0999920685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、franさんはどうしてあんなに\nサバイバル知識が豊富なんですか？　驚きましたよ",
      "startTime": 109.6333248932,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "いざという時……\n本気でお金がなくなったりした時のために学んだんです",
      "startTime": 116.3999915599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "最初は勉強のために読み始めたサバイバル漫画が\n思いのほか面白くてハマっちゃって",
      "startTime": 124.2666582266,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "何回も読んでたら、自然と知識が身に付いたんです",
      "startTime": 126.9095234949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、だから散策する時も、サバイバルすること\nになった時もちょっと楽しそうだったんですね",
      "startTime": 134.8999925772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですよ。悪いですか？",
      "startTime": 138.0441575288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "自己投資が無駄にならなかったんだから\nいいじゃないですか",
      "startTime": 143.2666673819,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "散策してた時は、漫画に描いてあった植物が生えてる！\nって興奮したんです。それだけですよ",
      "startTime": 149.3333340485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういう興味を持つのはとてもいいことだと思いますよ",
      "startTime": 153.4643381834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "……そういえば、{user}さん\n遭難したって分かった時、実は相当ビビってましたよね",
      "startTime": 160.8999925773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　い、いや、そんなことは……",
      "startTime": 166.7547322353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "分かってますよ、私を心配させまいと\n精一杯強がってくれたんですよね？",
      "startTime": 173.2666531404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "全部見透かされてたんですね……\nというか、わざわざ全部言わないで下さいよ",
      "startTime": 179.2666531404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "さて、そろそろ帰りますね\n明日がオフで助かりまし、た……",
      "startTime": 187.6333198071,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1400.010474499993,
          "startTime": 189.0333302816
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "あーーーーーーー！？",
      "startTime": 190.8183159271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "franさん！？　急にどうしたんですか！？\nもしかして無人島に何か忘れ物を……",
      "startTime": 195.1333198071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor022.m4a",
      "text": "株取引のこと、すっかり忘れてたぁ～\n持ってた株がいつの間にか暴落してる……嘘でしょ……",
      "startTime": 201.4333340486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_03-kor023.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと張り付いて見ておけば\n株価が落ち始めた時点でさっさと損切り出来たのに……",
      "startTime": 210.2333340486,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
